S.FORM: O Collage ko tatosa a romadiway i Taywan. I Collage ci Natsuko Lariyod aci Ông Ka-koân. Misanga' ciira to Pangcah/Amis, Sowal no Holam, Sowal no Nihon, ato Sowal no Amerika a romadiw. "Collagist" han ko haliCollage'ay a tamdaw. O Histori (Kongko) I 2018 a mihecaan, namidemak ciira to "Seikai Sakacecay - Ma'orip to fa'elohay a Shiken" no Band no 'Adingo ato The Bell. I 2019 a mihecaan, o ngangan no tatosa a romadiway ci "Collage" ciira a misatapang i Soni no Lalan (StreetVoice) ato Lalan no Simal (Youtube) I 2019 a mihecaan, saka3 a folad ira ko saka27 a romi'ad, misatapang a misanga' to radiw i "N1 Party - O Raradiw no Tamdaw no Nanguaq" ko Nanguaq, Payleday Records...
